  <goal>
    Cleanly refactored canvas state:
    1. All `sprk_nodetype` literal-string references replaced with `sprk_executortype` in `src/client/code-pages/PlaybookBuilder/src/**/*.{ts,tsx}`
    2. All `__actionType` injection hacks in `sprk_configjson` removed
    3. `PlaybookNodeData.type` (React Flow discriminator) PRESERVED — it's a UI-only field
    4. `PlaybookNodeData.executorType: number` is the new canonical dispatch field, round-trips to Dataverse `sprk_executortype` Choice
    5. `playbookNodeSync.ts` reads/writes `sprk_executortype` (not `sprk_nodetype`)
    6. Any graph traversal logic that branched on Node Type now branches on Executor Type
    7. Grep for `sprk_nodetype` in `src/client/code-pages/PlaybookBuilder/` returns ZERO hits (per FR-26 acceptance)
    8. Grep for `__actionType` returns ZERO hits
    9. Tests pass; canvas serializes new schema correctly
    10. Build passes (`npm run build:prod`)
  </goal>

